 &lt;h1 id=&#34;house-of-force&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#house-of-force&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; house-of-force&lt;/h1&gt;
